The accompanying pattern backer has a repeating heart pattern in pink, purple and white. Valentine’s day cards are the perfect way to send love and make up for missing the holiday rush of christmas and new years cards. It’s sometimes hard to get it all done and things have usually slowed down by Valentine’s day and you can plan sending out cards a little easier.
